dct_description_sm: Shows Romania (and surrounds) with Old Kingdom territory, before the treaties of 1917-1919.
Mittelbach's Verlag Leipzig ; Zeichung, Photolithographie u. Druck der graph. Kunstanstalt ,,Globus" Robert Mittelbach, Dresden-Kötzschenbroda.
Relief shown (at select peaks) by spot heights.
Shows various roads, railroads, cities and towns, borders, forts and fortresses, waterways.
